title: Are they for real? South Korean girl band offers glimpse into metaverse
description: At first glance, MAVE: looks like any other idolised K-pop band - except it only exists virtually.

title: Wall Street ends green as inflation cools, bank jitters ebb
description: NEW YORK (March 15): U.S. stocks bounced back on Tuesday as largely on-target inflation data and easing jitters over contagion in the banking sector cooled expectations regarding the size of the rate hike at the Federal Reserve's policy meeting next week. All three major U.S. stock indexes closed sharply higher, with the S&P 500 and the Dow gaining more than 1% and the tech-heavy Nasdaq surging more than 2%, after several sessions of risk-off turmoil driven by the fallout surrounding the implosion of Silicon Valley Bank and Signature Bank.
